title: Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 39
description:
Here's part 39 of these compilations with some really cool songs on it! Two songs I have put here are actually written by Vince Clarke, part of his unknown projects in the 80s. Let's see if you can find these songs; of course if you don't already know! Have fun listening and seed!
